Package com.upek.android.ptapi

Interface Summary
PtConnectionAdvancedI Extends PTAPI connection interface with advanced security operations.
PtConnectionI PTAPI connection interface.
PtConnectionManufacturingI Extends PTAPI connection interface with manufacturing operations.
PtGlobalI Main class with basic static Ptapi library methods.
 

Class Summary
PtConnection Represents one opened connection object.
PtConstants Contains all constants of PTApi package.
PtGlobal Main class with basic static Ptapi library methods.
PtUtil This class contains some utility functions for simplify some operations manipulating with structures stored in bytearray (original PT_DATA)
 

Exception Summary
PtException When any call of PTApi fails, this exception is throwed.
